description: This stunning 2BR/2BA top-floor condo in Peachtree Walk was completely renovated in 2023 and is a huge value opportunity for anyone looking for a stylish, functional and move-in ready condo with low HOA dues!  The open kitchen overlooks the 2-story great room flooded with natural light and includes Gaggenau stainless steel appliances and thoughtfully designed built-ins for maximum storage.   This freshly painted condo features a farm sink, white cabinetry, and luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout and an oversized ceiling fan upstairs.  A dramatic spiral staircase leads to a spacious loft and the second full bath - perfect as a guest room, home office or creative studio. Step out onto your covered balcony from the main-level primary suite for a view of the pool.  This residence also includes a separate storage space, assigned and gated parking with plenty of guest parking, and access to a host of amenities: pool, gym, dog park, bike locker, EV charging—all with low HOA fees. Stylish, functional, and move-in ready!
